new molecules=E2=80=94drugs, compounds for agriculture, or any other chemic=
al product=E2=80=94we rely on complex industrial systems that create far mo=
re waste than desired. Our approach to construction has escalating costs an=
d can=E2=80=99t scale to support a growing population.
