ipeline&#8212;which stand the chance to become blockbuster drugs with marke=
t exclusivity if they are approved. Approved assets are primarily sold to m=
ajor pharmaceutical companies.</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16=
px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;"><text>From a business strategy p=
erspective, this has meant that most </text><strong>value capture</strong><=
text> comes from pursuing highly specific vertical solutions&#8212;new drug=
